Package: arrayQualityMetrics
Version: 1.0.1
Title: Quality Metrics and Quality Report Generator for Microarrays
Author: Audrey Kauffmann, Wolfgang Huber
Maintainer: Audrey Kauffmann <audrey@ebi.ac.uk>
Depends: R (>= 2.5.0), methods, Biobase, arrayMagic, geneplotter, vsn, RColorBrewer, affyPLM, CCl4
Description: This package performs quality metrics on AffyBatch, ExpressionSet,
		 NchannelSet, containing microarray data from any platforms, 
		 one or two channels. The results are designated to allow the 
		 user to rapidly assess the quality of a set of arrays.
Reference: TBA
License: The Artistic License, Version 2.0
LazyLoad: Yes
biocViews: Microarray, Preprocessing, Visualization

